the times I've needed them.

290
00:13:42,466 --> 00:13:44,033
oh, here's a card.

291
00:13:44,433 --> 00:13:45,866
[humming]

292
00:13:48,433 --> 00:13:50,533
from Mr. Thomas fennel,
Tavistock square.

293
00:13:50,933 --> 00:13:51,932
what a place to live.

294
00:13:52,133 --> 00:13:53,832
who the hell do you suppose he is, Evie?

295
00:13:54,033 --> 00:13:55,632
oh, some feller knocked all of a heap

296
00:13:55,833 --> 00:13:57,899
by your fatal beauty, I expect.

297
00:13:58,399 --> 00:13:59,732
probably cost a fortune.

298
