went without dinner for a week.

299
00:14:02,266 --> 00:14:03,866
oh, pull the other one.

300
00:14:05,466 --> 00:14:06,932
[man singing]

301
00:14:07,133 --> 00:14:09,065
beginners, please, miss Lambert.

302
00:14:09,266 --> 00:14:09,866
mmm-hmm.

303
00:14:09,866 --> 00:14:11,698
well, whoever Mr. Thomas fennel is,

304
00:14:11,899 --> 00:14:13,132
I think it's all right

305
00:14:13,333 --> 00:14:15,132
having a young man send me flowers

306
00:14:15,333 --> 00:14:16,598
at my time of life.

307
00:14:16,799 --> 00:14:18,032
I mean, it
just shows you--

308
00:14:18,233 --> 00:14:19,899
how do you know he's a young man?

309
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,733
he's probably over 80.

310
00:14:23,166 --> 00:14:24,566
go to hell.

311
00:14:27,133 --> 00:14:28,699
[band playing]

312
00:14:37,899 --> 00:14:39,666
